# FinE Companion — environment example (no secrets).
#
# The app needs NO secrets or API keys. The only build-time variable is the
# GitHub Pages base path, which the deploy workflow sets automatically from the
# repository name. Set it manually only for a local subpath preview.
#
# Local default (root):        VITE_BASE_PATH=/
# GitHub project Pages value:  VITE_BASE_PATH=/<repository-name>/
VITE_BASE_PATH=/
